  virt-viewer-0.6.0.ebuild:
  ~x86 keyworded, see bug 513116

*virt-viewer-2.0 (19 Jan 2015)

  19 Jan 2015; Matthias Maier <tamiko@gentoo.org> +virt-viewer-2.0.ebuild,
  virt-viewer-0.6.0.ebuild, virt-viewer-1.0.ebuild:
  version bump; fix file collision in >=0.6.0, bug #515488, patch by Christian
  Ruppert (idl0r)

*virt-viewer-1.0 (21 Sep 2014)

  21 Sep 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +virt-viewer-1.0.ebuild:
  NMU: Version bump. Fixes bug #519642.

