  +files/virt-viewer-0.6.0-fix-c99-compat.patch,
  -files/virt-viewer-0.6.0-require-C99.patch, virt-viewer-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Use alternative patch from Christophe Fergeau for pre-c99 compat.

